{"product_id":"madara-spf30-plant-stem-cell-age-defying-face-sunscreen-40ml","title":"MÁDARA SPF30 Plant Stem Cell Age-Defying Face Sunscreen 40ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003eIngredients from natural origin meet cellular biology to create this break-through daily sunscreen that provides high level protection with an invisible, flawless nude skin finish. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003eInnovative formula with patent pending stem cells from Northern Dragonhead deliver a hyper dose of antioxidants to completely shield the skin from urban pollution while also regenerating and protecting the skin microbiome for an age-defying effect.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003eThe ultra-light, subtly tinted texture infused with hyaluronic acid and SPF-boosting raspberry seed oil glides onto the skin easily, leaving no white marks. Utmost protection for a forever sun kissed look.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to clean skin or over your daily moisturiser. Reapply if necessary during the day.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Zinc Oxide, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe) Leaf Juice, Dicaprylyl Carbonate, Isoamyl Laurate, Lecithin, Polyglyceryl-3 ricinoleate, Glycerin, Butylene Glycol, Sorbitan olivate, Aqua, CI 77891 (Titanium Dioxide), Oryza Sativa (Rice) Bran Oil, Vegetable Oil, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Wax, Oryza Sativa (Rice) Bran Wax, Rhus Succedanea Fruit Wax, Hydrated Silica, Aroma, Sodium Chloride, Xanthan Gum, Sorbitan Caprylate, Jojoba Esters, Citric acid, Propanediol, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Dracocephalum Ruyschiana (Dragonhead) Cell Culture Extract, Polyhydroxystearic Acid, Rubus Idaeus (Raspberry) Seed Oil, Caprylyl glycol, Benzoic Acid, Tocopherol, Ascorbyl Palmitate, CI 77491 (Iron Oxides), CI 77492 (Iron Oxides), CI 77499 (Iron Oxides), Sodium phytate, Camellia Sinensis (Green Tea) Leaf Extract, Quercus Robur (Oak) Bark Extract, Vitis Vinifera (Grape) Seed Extract, Isostearic Acid, Polyglyceryl-3 Polyricinoleate, Sodium Benzoate, Hydrolyzed Hyaluronic Acid, Sodium Hyaluronate, Potassium Sorbate, Propylene Glycol, Limonene, Benzyl Salicylate, Citral, Linalool, Eugenol\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e* Please note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49887709102407,"sku":null,"price":32.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-spf30-plant-stem-cell-age-defying-face-sunscreen-40ml-514512.jpg?v=1739897254","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/madara-spf30-plant-stem-cell-age-defying-face-sunscreen-40ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}